import React from 'react';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import styled from 'styled-components';
import Card from './Card';

const CardWrapper = styled(Card)`
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);
`


const UserInfo = () => (
    <CardWrapper>
        <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Person uppgifter</Card.Title>
        <Form.Row>
            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridEmail">
                <Form.Label>Mail</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="name@example.com" />
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group as={Col}>
                <Form.Label>Välj fil</Form.Label>
                <Form.File id="custom-file" label="Ladda upp foto" data-browse="Bläddra" custom />
            </Form.Group>
        </Form.Row>

        <Form.Row>
            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="firstName">
                <Form.Label>Förnamn</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="Karl" />
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="lastName">
                <Form.Label>Efternamn</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="Jansson" />
            </Form.Group>
        </Form.Row>

        <Form.Row>
            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="title">
                <Form.Label>Titel</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="Lärare"/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="phone">
                <Form.Label>Telefonnummer</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="+46760042332"/>
            </Form.Group>
        </Form.Row>
        </Card.Body>
    </CardWrapper>
)



export default UserInfo
